00:36:26,430 --> 00:36:27,270
Xia Qingsheng?

764
00:36:28,870 --> 00:36:29,710
Xia Qingsheng!

765
00:36:30,910 --> 00:36:32,060
Bangunlah, Xia Qingsheng.

766
00:36:32,060 --> 00:36:32,900
bangun.

767
00:36:34,220 --> 00:36:35,190
Itu sahaja yang anda boleh minum?

768
00:36:52,830 --> 00:36:53,670
Kapten Meng,

769
00:36:54,060 --> 00:36:55,580
Komandan Xia tidak dapat menahan minuman kerasnya.

770
00:36:56,060 --> 00:36:57,100
- Jom minum.
- Pasti.

771
00:36:57,100 --> 00:36:57,940
Ayuh.

772
00:37:00,140 --> 00:37:01,060
- Minum.
- Ceria.

773
00:37:01,060 --> 00:37:01,900
Ayuh.

774
00:37:25,540 --> 00:37:27,140
Jika anda bebas,

775
00:37:27,870 --> 00:37:28,870
boleh awak tukar

776
00:37:31,140 --> 00:37:32,310
pakaian saya lagi?

777
00:37:35,580 --> 00:37:36,870
Saya telah duduk berjam-jam.

778
00:37:37,830 --> 00:37:38,910
Luka saya berdarah lagi.

779
00:37:39,830 --> 00:37:40,670
Sakit sangat.

780
00:37:41,690 --> 00:37:43,470
Ambil deria sentuhan saya sekarang.

781
00:37:45,180 --> 00:37:46,100
Sakit adalah cara manusia

782
00:37:46,100 --> 00:37:47,180
daripada melindungi diri mereka sendiri.

783
00:37:48,180 --> 00:37:49,180
Jika anda tidak berasa sakit,

784
00:37:49,580 --> 00:37:50,990
bahaya hanya akan bertambah.

785
00:38:03,750 --> 00:38:05,270
Apabila menembusi musuh

786
00:38:05,580 --> 00:38:06,910
dan menghadapi Lima Belas,

787
00:38:07,530 --> 00:38:09,270
awak seperti roh yang tiada perasaan.

788
00:38:10,020 --> 00:38:11,830
Dan sekarang awak menangis.

789
00:38:14,750 --> 00:38:15,700
saya suka sangat.

790
00:38:25,990 --> 00:38:27,020
macam mana?

791
00:38:36,240 --> 00:38:41,570
♪Antara hitam dan putih,
riak terlintas♪

792
00:38:41,900 --> 00:38:46,150
♪Bayang terjumpa cahaya♪

793
00:38:47,510 --> 00:38:52,880
♪Ia menembusi kegelapan dan masa♪

794
00:38:53,180 --> 00:38:57,780
♪Nasib yang tidak dapat dipecahkan♪

795
00:38:58,870 --> 00:39:00,710
♪Tiba-tiba retak♪

796
00:39:12,920 --> 00:39:18,360
♪Antara hitam dan putih,
riak terlintas♪

797
00:39:18,540 --> 00:39:22,870
♪Bayang terjumpa cahaya♪

798
00:39:24,240 --> 00:39:29,630
♪Ia menembusi kegelapan dan masa♪

799
00:39:29,860 --> 00:39:33,800
♪Nasib yang tidak dapat dipecahkan♪

800
00:39:35,570 --> 00:39:37,460
♪Tiba-tiba retak♪

801
00:39:40,120 --> 00:39:43,280
♪Dengar, semua bunyi menderu♪

802
00:39:43,280 --> 00:39:45,810
♪Ketika ais sejuk bertukar menjadi air pasang♪

803
00:39:45,810 --> 00:39:51,330
♪Kesunyian seabad meleburkan impian♪

804
00:39:51,330 --> 00:39:54,570
♪Mengikut hidayah takdir♪

805
00:39:54,570 --> 00:39:59,430
♪Dengan takdir, detik-detik kami bertukar♪

806
00:39:59,770 --> 00:40:02,790
♪Jantung bangun tiba-tiba♪

807
00:40:02,790 --> 00:40:05,610
♪Tonton bunga api jatuh seperti bintang♪

808
00:40:05,870 --> 00:40:08,400
♪Ikatan ini berselirat menjadi benang♪

809
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:13,820
♪Pantulan dunia menjadi kabus♪

810
00:40:13,990 --> 00:40:17,060
♪Meminjam satu degupan jantung sekejap♪

811
00:40:17,220 --> 00:40:22,120
♪Anda menarik saya ke dalam debu fana,
sehingga saya terpikat dengan pesonanya♪

812
00:40:22,330 --> 00:40:25,800
♪Jantung bangun tiba-tiba♪

